  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then I was-- in Philharmonic, I was working.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Keo.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Keo.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, it's Jewish.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Keo, K-E-O, Keo.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You see, in the beginning, I was assistant with them.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then I became independent by myself.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And when I was working for myself, we-- like, like a variety group, singer, accordion, different kind of variety group.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I  have  my magic tricks.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My performance was 20 minutes in a stage, which you always have better paid.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The longer on you're on the stage, you get more paid.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we was a group of 18 people, 20 people.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I am a [RUSSIAN], too-- [RUSSIAN].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[RUSSIAN].",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This is-- you're laying down.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And you work with the feet.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You're turning over--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, another person.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, it's similar, a little bit connected.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was working with them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then [RUSSIAN]-- I found out I'm not very talented.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I saw people much better from me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I saw that I will never reach the talent what they have.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I decided to step out from this and just magic.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This was what I make a living in Russia, up the whole way-- up to the-- up to 19-- 1955-- up to 1954.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, you see, after the war, there was not too many-- the Russian didn't trust too many performers to go overseas.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was in Poland.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But Poland, Poland was communistic.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I was in Bucharest, in Romania.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was communist.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They let us out for concerts.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You know, like, in the capitalist countries, no, I didn't travel.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You see, after I was-- something I say, I was involved with against the Russian law.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it was a court-- witnesses-- what I say.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And this-- and what I say what was fighting, who was wrong, was not worded.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
